{"tid":1873474,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[填表師召集] 又係醫護篤灰Secrets，4 招拆解","createTime":"2020-02-10T16:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T13:54:46.000Z","uid":52090,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c2f3ebbf0f23f9474b3e10678ca56fffbf485949","tid":1873474,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T16:35:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HA-Normal-Secrets-105351077591107/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHA-Normal-Secrets-105351077591107%2F&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4VEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=e741d87a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HA-Normal-Secrets-105351077591107/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1bbiWhxEhvXVUWfyVzjm5ejbAjwDtCCkVpzpQdnCwtuw/viewform?edit_requested=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2F1bbiWhxEhvXVUWfyVzjm5ejbAjwDtCCkVpzpQdnCwtuw%2Fviewform%3Fedit_requested%3Dtrue&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4VEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=c260d23f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1bbiWhxEhvXVUWfyVzjm5ejbAjwDtCCkVpzpQdnCwtuw/viewform?edit_requested=true</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>請幫忙Report Facebook及Google Form</strong><br />\nGoogle Form基本上有4招拆解方法<br />\n<br />\n1. 基本式：Report 表格，保護私隱<br />\n需時最長，但效果最強<br />\n<br />\n2. 車輪戰：不停填Form，填到爆Form<br />\n簡單方便，以量取勝，但對家容易處理<br />\n<br />\n3. 反間計：以藍絲口吻，篤灰藍醫護，以假亂真<br />\n以假亂真，令對方分唔出真篤灰，以保護手足<br />\n<br />\n4. 美人計：如果表格可以上傳檔案，以無數AV上傳，以迫爆15GB容量<br />\n行動快速，令表格不能再填寫<br />\n副檔名限制 &gt; .mp4 改成 .jpg<br />\n連結類 &gt; 噁心影片 / jump scare 影片<br />\nSize限制 &gt; 壓縮影片，換成圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成功例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EAWVzsG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEAWVzsG.png&h=5ed7e825&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[全世界入黎] 對抗篤灰醫護網，有三招拆解<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1868502/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1868502/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n香港獨立，唯一出路</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"328bb3af3946e7fc09d32f2ccfc120d5558ffb22","tid":1873474,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T16:36:46.000Z","msg":"歷史分析，教你回應藍絲<br />\n「已經變質，爭取民主要放火破壞咩？」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1742188/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1742188/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"86edeaf78344de9d8867b7449002a4ee9f386219","tid":1873474,"uid":22088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T16:37:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e6b32a3d067db1207ffa4164952c54ad1434e81f","tid":1873474,"uid":122122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T16:37:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c527e42dde8034c3e7819cb16d5ebd194f167522","tid":1873474,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T16:38:27.000Z","msg":"[正視聽] 肺炎令到運動冷卻？根本18區都黃藍齊齊開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1871186/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1871186/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"fb7655d40a180f4b2b9a8def582b99f1e4393898","tid":1873474,"uid":46271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T16:38:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3df2e6f0cd230ff8508dc0a864ea505d9d4f4e15","tid":1873474,"uid":341649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T16:39:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de0f57defdf1186168ead7e56c4de116821fe55","ti